WIP

docker volume create yacht
docker run -d -p 8000:8000 -v /var/run/docker.sock:/var/run/docker.sock -v yacht:/config --name yacht selfhostedpro/yacht

This will start Yacht on port 8000 (change this to 8001 if you're also using portainer).

The default login is admin@yacht.local and pass you should change this immediately by clicking on admin in the top right and then "User" then select 
"Change Password" in the top menu. You can also change your username using this field.
